Room in 2BR, Morningside Heights
$1,225 - New York, New York

Spacious, furnished room in a 2BR apartment, only a 2 minute walk from Columbia's Morningside campus and 10mins from 1, A, B, C, and D trains. 

The room features a comfy bed, a reading nook with a soft chair, a bookshelf, a vanity, and a work/study space. The closet and dresser space is ample, and bedding will be provided. The shared living area is nice and welcoming, suitable both for quiet work/reading and hosting a small gathering. Microwave, coffee machine and blender are available in the kitchen, as well as lots of dishes and pots.

Friendly doormen are around 24-hours, the super lives in the building, and there's the extra perk of not having to take out (household) trash - just leave it in front of the apartment door between 10pm and 7am. The laundry room is in the building.
